{"title":"广告计划","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3080","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>公司最近生产出一种新产品，正准备上市销售，广告部也准备了相应的宣传广告以增加销售量。现在已知新产品有宣传广告和无宣传广告的预期收入以及广告的费用，请你编程来决定是否需要使用广告来宣传这个新产品</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行为t表示测试数据组数。<br>接下来t行，每行三个数字r,e和c，分别表示新产品无宣传广告的预期收入、有宣传广告的预期收入以及宣传广告的费用</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>对于每个输入数据，输出一行字符串：如果宣传广告后收入增加，则输出&ldquo;profit&rdquo;；如果宣传广告后收入降低，则输出&ldquo;deficit&rdquo;，如果宣传广告后，收支平衡，则输出&ldquo;balance&rdquo;。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3<br>0 100 70</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>profit</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>t(1≤t≤10000)，</p>\n<p>−106≤r,e≤106 ,0≤c≤106。</p>\n<p>很小</p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}